<scopecontent encodinganalog="520">
<p>The PDepartment of Recreational Sports publications (.5 linear foot) includes annual reports, pamphlets and brochures, calendars, manuals such as the Recreational Sports Program and Policy Guide, and schedules such as the Recreational Drop-In Schedule. Also included manuals from the intramural sports program.  Thue Pubications are organized into two two series:  Unit Publications and Sub-Unit Publications.</p>
</scopecontent>

