<dsc type="combined">

<c01 level="series"><did><unittitle>Unit Publications</unittitle></did>
<scopecontent>
<p>The Unit Publications subseries includes annual reports covering the years 1976 through 1977 and 1985 through 1991, brochures, and calendars.  Manuals under various titles such as <title render="italic">Intramural and Recreational Sports Handbook</title> (1974-1975), <title render="italic">Recreational Sports Program and Policy</title> (1978-1979), and <title render="italic"> Recreational Sports Program and Policy Guide</title> (scattered issues from 1980 to 1992) date from 1974 to 1992.  They describe the various programs within and the policies of the department.  Schedules for the recreational drop-in programs cover the period from 1977 to 1995.</p></scopecontent>
